claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A section of the article’s metadata including article history (received, revised, accepted dates, online availability) and keywords (Influenza vaccine; Baculovirus expression; Recombinant protein; Clinical trials). Note: The page is article metadata, not a figure or data table, so it offers no relevant evidence regarding antigenic match.
